quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,"Tẽngã sã n wa rĩms a rĩms-kεgengã."
  99,2,"Tɩ Tẽngã yiis a zɩɩbã."
  99,3,"Tɩ ninsaalã yeele ""yaa bõe n tar-a?"""
  99,4,"Raarã a togsda a kibayã."
  99,5,"Ad fo Soabã n lεεms-a woto."
  99,6,"Ra-kãngã, nebã yita kõbg toor-toore, tɩ b na n wilg-b b tʋʋmã."
  99,7,"Rẽnd ned ning sẽn wa n tʋm-a sẽn paood to-to fãa, tɩ yaa sõma, a yãt-a lame."
  99,8,"La ned ning sẽn wa n tʋm-a sẽn paood to-to fãa, tɩ yaa wẽnga, a yãt-a lame"
